metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Sky Road - Zone 1 is more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion: Sky Road - Zone 1 has sections analyzed in the following keys: D Mixolydian, D Phrygian, D Major,  and D Minor.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: Why make the key D Phrygian when you're gonna make every note and chord that of D minor
